Easy TOAST

In your app-level build.gradle, add compile "org.jetbrains.anko:anko-common:0.8.3"

Syntax:
toast("Hi there!")
toast(R.string.message)
longToast("Wow, such a duration")

Android Studio should auto generate but you can "import org.jetbrains.anko.toast" and/or "import org.jetbrains.anko.longToast" to your Activity.
